Installation Instructions
-------------------------


Dependencies
-----------------------

qt4-dev
libsqlite3-dev
cmake-2.4 (this is the build system used)
libginac-1.3.7
gsl-1.9
OpenCascade6.2
boost C++ libraries (only use shared_ptr.hpp)


Build and run instructions
----------------------------

1. set CASROOT and OPENCASCADE_LINK_DIR environment variables
2. run cmake
3. run make
4. execute ark3d


Example build and run process
------------------------------------

export CASROOT=~/download/opencascade/Linux/ros
export OPENCASCADE_LINK_DIR=/opt/OpenCASCADE-6.2/lib
cmake .
make
export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=/opt/OpenCASCADE-6.2/lib
export CSF_GraphicShr=/opt/OpenCASCADE-6.2/lib/libTKOpenGl.so
./src/Interface/ark3d



